south african foreign reserv up sharpli in feb south africa 's total gold and foreign asset rose by 700 mln rand in februari to 6.2 billion rand after rise by almost one billion rand in januari , reserv bank governor gerhard de kock said . de kock , interview on state-run televis , gave no breakdown of the reserv . he also said that to curb inflat , salari increas would have to be below the inflat rate . the state must set an exampl by keep wage increas below the inflat rate , he said . consum price rose by 16.1 pct in the year to januari .